Bayer Intends to Delist From London Stock Exchange Main Market

-- B y   M a r i a j o s e   V e r a
-- 
2011-09-26T12:20:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-26/bayer-intends-to-delist-from-london-stock-exchange-main-market.html
Bayer AG (BAYN)  plans to delist its
securities from the Main Market of the  London  Stock Exchange due
to their low trading volume and the administrative costs
associated with the listing. Bayer expects the shares to delist
from London with effect from market opening on Oct. 25.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Mariajose Vera at 
 mvera1@bloomberg.net  